title: 5 Unforgettable Jutsu From Naruto - Comicbook.com
text:
5 Unforgettable Jutsu From Naruto Megan Peters Slide of 
Naruto has been around for well over a decade, and the franchise is still trucking along. 
The series may have ended its primary manga already, but a spin-off is underway along with its anime . Naruto Shippuden is getting ready to bid fans farewell have years on air, but a sequel show will take its place days later. So, as a new era dawns upon the Naruto fandom, it is time fans looked back and paid respect to how awesome the series has been. 
Over its course, Naruto Uzumaki and his comrades have taken on some insane villains and made up even crazier offenses. The catalog of secret jutsu has likely doubled if not tripled since the hero’s class graduated the academy. 
Here at ComicBook, we are taking a moment to recognize some of the best that the anime has to offer. In the following slides, you’ll find five totally unforgettable jutsu techniques from Naruto , and you will be left wishing you had your own chakra stores to test out.
